        "content": "About API of the National Bank of Ukraine (NBU)\nhttps://bank.gov.ua/ua/open-data/api-dev\n\nExample: https://bank.gov.ua/NBU_Exchange/exchange_site?start=20220115&end=20220131&sort=exchangedate&order=asc&json\nSet  *start  date - 20260101*  and  *end date  - now*\n\n",
